title: Week 9 recap
itunes:title: Week 9 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler, Dan Hanzus and Colleen Wolfe – break down all the action from Week 9 of the regular season, including an NFC East showdown in overtime between the Cowboys and the Eagles, and the Colts handing the Broncos their first loss of the season.
